<emph>
P0134: O2 Sensor Circuit No Activity Detected (Sensor 1)
</emph>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Output voltage of HO2S-1 circuit stays between m 0.42 and 0.50 V for 15 sec.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
(3 D/C detection logic)
</ptxt>
</entry>
